---
title: Creamy Mushroom Ragu over Polenta Cakes with Arugula Salad
description: Precooked polenta is truly a gift: the work of turning it nice and creamy has already been done, meaning that you can focus on taking it to the next level. Here, that means searing it in a pan until it gets nice and creamy on the outside and tantalizingly tender on the inside. With a creamy mushroom sauce on top and a balsamic-dressed salad to the side, that amounts to nothing less than polenta perfection.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-mushroom-ragu-2de0bd53.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/creamy-mushroom-ragu-5ba83dcd.pdf
